{"tid":2319054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"終於搞facebook!!! 我侵有仇必報真君子!","createTime":"2020-12-09T23:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T03:12:02.000Z","uid":263025,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bd87cd7d275a65024d8b133266f1c90df0f8f4","tid":2319054,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cp24.com/world/us-government-states-file-antitrust-action-against-facebook-1.5223979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cp24.com%2Fworld%2Fus-government-states-file-antitrust-action-against-facebook-1.5223979&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=6e953ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cp24.com/world/us-government-states-file-antitrust-action-against-facebook-1.5223979</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zEpoqjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEpoqjg.jpg&h=20ca508a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華盛頓--美國政府和48個州週三起訴Facebook，指責其濫用在社交網路中的市場力量來壓制較小的競爭對手，並尋求補救措施，其中可能包括強制剝離該社交網路的Instagram和WhatsApp等的消息服務。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦貿易委員會和紐約總檢察長萊蒂西亞-詹姆斯宣佈的這一具有里程碑意義的反壟斷訴訟，標誌著今年政府對看似不可撼動的科技巨頭的第二次重大攻勢。司法部在10月起訴谷歌濫用其在線上搜索和廣告領域的主導地位--這是自20年前對微軟提起歷史性訴訟以來，政府為遏制競爭所做的最重要嘗試。亞馬遜和蘋果也因涉嫌反競爭行為而受到國會和聯邦當局的調查。<br />\n<br />\n詹姆斯在新聞發佈會上指出，&quot;我們阻止這種掠奪性收購公司的行為，恢復市場信心，這真的是至關重要的。&quot;"},{"pid":"d6a03c11f7ed2f9a1ed53ee002438bb42d0a056f","tid":2319054,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc548d322603ffb7ae48f67773a3197120604632","tid":2319054,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T23:52:43.000Z","msg":"剩低兩個無告既州係咪加州同紐約州<img src=\"/assets/f